</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p>Where “\u05d1” is unicode for the Hebrew letter “Bet” , so it would be better to first see whether NLTK can process the text in this format.</p>

<p>Bad news, there’s no hebrew tokenizer in my nltk installation :</p>

